        </div>
Crossroad Towers boasts BRAND NEW three bedroom and two bedroom/two bath apartments in Baldwin. We offer beautiful floor to ceiling windows, crown molding, in suite washer and dryers, all stainless steel appliances. Our four story buildings all have an elevator for easy access to your front door! Enjoy our state of the art fitness center and swimming pool. <ol type="Beautiful brand new 1 BR, 1 BA condo for rent in convenient country setting in excellent neighborhood between Cambridge and New Concord. Features all new appliances, private backyard, peaceful patio, and all one level entrances with private parking. Conveniently located 3-5 minutes to I70 or I77, approx. 7 min. to towns, stores, and restaurants of Cambridge or New Concord. Seneca Lake and Salt Fork State Park approx. 20 minutes. This must see condo includes washer and dryer, dishwasher, lawn care service, and WiFi. On site management care. Central A/C and gas heat. $895.00 / month plus utilities. Utilities budget of $200.00 per mo. which includes electric, gas, water/sewage, and trash disposal to be paid each month directly to Landlord. Security deposit required. 3 mo. lease availability. No HUD. This is a non-smoking and no pets property. Serious inquiries only and application fee of $20.00 for background check may apply.Spectacular redone garden style apartment is a great place to call home.4501 Hammersley Road, Madison WI 537111 Bedroom garden style apartment $975 per month - plus utilitiesAvailable 9/1-Laminate flooring in entry, kitchen, and bath-Stainless steel appliance package to include dishwasher, microwave, range, and fridge-Large pantry off kitchen-Dining room-2 Oversized closets in bedroom-Patio overlooks the courtyard area-In-wall unit air conditioning-Digital Laundry-Large storage is available and is included-en-suite bathroom-Cat friendly with pet deposit, $10 per month pet feeFree off-street parking,garage parkingisavailable at an additional fee"></ol><br>
